        "\n",
        "# Building the Generator\n",
        "\n",
        "## Context Construction\n",
        "\n",
        "Good generation depends on how context is packed:\n",
        "\n",
        "- rank and select chunks\n",
        "- deduplicate and compress\n",
        "- preserve source attribution\n",
        "- format prompt sections clearly\n",
        "\n",
        "---\n",
        "\n",
        "## Prompt Template Pattern"
      ],
      "id": "8dfed4c4"
    },
    {
      "cell_type": "code",
      "metadata": {},
      "source": [
        "#| eval: false\n",
        "from langchain.prompts import ChatPromptTemplate\n",
        "\n",
        "RAG_PROMPT = ChatPromptTemplate.from_template(\n",
        "  \"\"\"\n",
        "  You are a careful assistant.\n",
        "  Use ONLY the context to answer.\n",
        "\n",
        "  Question:\n",
        "  {question}\n",
        "\n",
        "  Context:\n",
        "  {context}\n",
        "\n",
        "  If context is insufficient, say so explicitly.\n",
        "  \"\"\"\n",
        ")"
      ],
      "id": "3c882af1",
      "execution_count": null,
      "outputs": []
    },
    {
      "cell_type": "markdown",
      "metadata": {},
      "source": [
        "---\n",
        "\n",
        "## Response Contract\n",
        "\n",
        "Production answer format should include:\n",
        "\n",
        "- concise claim\n",
        "- evidence bullets\n",
        "- confidence note\n",
        "- citations or source IDs\n",
        "\n",
        "This supports grading, auditing, and stakeholder trust.\n",
        "\n",
        "# NVIDIA Patterns to Reuse\n",
        "\n",
        "## Ingestion and Chunking"
      ],
      "id": "28da2fe3"
    },
    {
      "cell_type": "code",
      "metadata": {},
      "source": [
        "#| eval: false\n",
        "from langchain_community.document_loaders import DirectoryLoader\n",
        "from langchain.text_splitter import RecursiveCharacterTextSplitter\n",
        "\n",
        "docs = DirectoryLoader(\"./data/corpus\", glob=\"**/*.md\").load()\n",
        "splitter = RecursiveCharacterTextSplitter(chunk_size=700, chunk_overlap=120)\n",
        "chunks = splitter.split_documents(docs)"
      ],
      "id": "7ba03c70",
      "execution_count": null,
      "outputs": []
    },
    {
      "cell_type": "markdown",
      "metadata": {},
      "source": [
        "---\n",
        "\n",
        "## Embeddings and Vector Store"
      ],
      "id": "e50111eb"
    },
    {
      "cell_type": "code",
      "metadata": {},
      "source": [
        "#| eval: false\n",
        "from langchain_nvidia_ai_endpoints import NVIDIAEmbeddings\n",
        "from langchain_community.vectorstores import FAISS\n",
        "\n",
        "embed = NVIDIAEmbeddings(model=\"nvidia/nv-embedqa-e5-v5\")\n",
        "vs = FAISS.from_documents(chunks, embed)\n",
        "retriever = vs.as_retriever(search_type=\"similarity\", search_kwargs={\"k\": 5})"
      ],
      "id": "0b91ee90",
      "execution_count": null,
      "outputs": []
    },
    {
      "cell_type": "markdown",
      "metadata": {},
      "source": [
        "---\n",
        "\n",
        "## LCEL RAG Chain"
      ],
      "id": "b66132b4"
    },
    {
      "cell_type": "code",
      "metadata": {},
      "source": [
        "#| eval: false\n",
        "from langchain_nvidia_ai_endpoints import ChatNVIDIA\n",
        "from langchain_core.runnables import RunnableLambda\n",
        "from langchain_core.output_parsers import StrOutputParser\n",
        "\n",
        "llm = ChatNVIDIA(model=\"meta/llama-3.1-70b-instruct\")\n",
        "\n",
        "def join_context(docs):\n",
        "  return \"\\n\\n\".join(d.page_content for d in docs)\n",
        "\n",
        "chain = (\n",
        "  {\n",
        "    \"question\": RunnableLambda(lambda x: x[\"question\"]),\n",
        "    \"context\": RunnableLambda(lambda x: join_context(retriever.invoke(x[\"question\"]))),\n",
        "  }\n",
        "  | RAG_PROMPT\n",
        "  | llm\n",
        "  | StrOutputParser()\n",
        ")"
      ],
      "id": "b47af718",
      "execution_count": null,
      "outputs": []
    },
    {
      "cell_type": "markdown",
