      "source": [
        "# Evaluation and Diagnostics\n",
        "\n",
        "## A Practical Evaluation Matrix\n",
        "\n",
        "Track both quality and operations:\n",
        "\n",
        "- answer relevance\n",
        "- groundedness / faithfulness\n",
        "- citation quality\n",
        "- latency\n",
        "- cost per query\n",
        "- retrieval hit quality\n",
        "\n",
        "---\n",
        "\n",
        "## LLM-as-a-Judge Loop"
      ],
      "id": "f59d86ae"
    },
    {
      "cell_type": "code",
      "metadata": {},
      "source": [
        "#| eval: false\n",
        "judge_prompt = \"\"\"\n",
        "Rate the answer from 1-5 for groundedness and relevance.\n",
        "Question: {q}\n",
        "Answer: {a}\n",
        "Reference: {ref}\n",
        "Return JSON.\n",
        "\"\"\""
      ],
      "id": "702d1e30",
      "execution_count": null,
      "outputs": []
    },
    {
      "cell_type": "markdown",
      "metadata": {},
      "source": [
        "Use sampled human checks to calibrate the judge and detect drift.\n",
        "\n",
        "---\n",
        "\n",
        "## Error Taxonomy\n",
        "\n",
        "- retrieval miss: right info absent\n",
        "- retrieval noise: irrelevant chunk dominates\n",
        "- synthesis failure: answer conflicts with evidence\n",
        "- abstention failure: should have said \"insufficient context\"\n",
        "\n",
        "Each error type implies a different fix path.\n",
        "\n",
        "# Productionization\n",
        "\n",
        "## Serving with LangServe + FastAPI"
      ],
      "id": "ca83704f"
    },
    {
      "cell_type": "code",
      "metadata": {},
      "source": [
        "#| eval: false\n",
        "from fastapi import FastAPI\n",
        "from langserve import add_routes\n",
        "\n",
        "app = FastAPI(title=\"AD698-RAG\")\n",
        "add_routes(app, chain, path=\"/rag\")"
      ],
